function Nd2(props) {
    const { Img, title } = props;
    return ( <
        div className = "nd_item_2" >
        <
        div className = "item_img_2" >
        <
        a href = "true" >
        <
        img src = { Img }
        alt = "true" / >
        <
        /a> <
        /div> <
        div className = "item_title_2" >
        <
        div className = "title_time_2" >
        <
        ul >
        <
        li > VNPT < /li> <li> . </li > < li > 6 giờ trước < /li> <
        /ul> <
        /div> <
        div className = "title_title_2" >
        <
        a href = "true" >
        <
        p > { title } <
        /p> <
        /a> <
        /div> <
        div className = "title_icon_2" >
        <
        span style = {
            { marginRight: 10 } } >
        0 & nbsp; < i className = "far fa-thumbs-up" / >
        <
        /span> <
        span >
        0 & nbsp; < i className = "far fa-comment" / >
        <
        /span> <
        /div> <
        /div> <
        /div>
    );
}
export default Nd2;
